    <section>
        <h2>The Beauty of Mountain Landscapes</h2>
        <p>Mountain landscapes are among the most awe-inspiring sights on Earth. From towering peaks to serene 
            valleys, mountains provide a dramatic backdrop that can leave you speechless. 
            The ever-changing weather, the rugged terrain, and the expansive views make mountain landscapes ideal for 
            hiking, photography, and simply appreciating nature's grandeur.</p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
        <h2>The Tranquility of Coastal Landscapes</h2>
        <p>Coastal landscapes offer a completely different kind of beauty. 
            The sound of crashing waves, the salty breeze, and the vast horizon create a sense of peace and relaxation. 
            Whether it's a rugged cliffside, a sandy beach, or a rocky coastline, the combination of water, 
            land, and sky never fails to captivate the senses.</p>
    </section>
